data.description: 4 BEDROOM HOME in SW Cape Coral. Looking for a new construction home but don't want to wait the many months it takes for one to be built for you. Move your stuff in & start living your best life since all the systems in this home are like new. Inside, revel the offering both style & easy maintenance. The floor plan makes extraordinary use of modest square footage. The spacious kitchen and family room serve as the heart of the home. Tucked away at the rear of the home for privacy, the master suite dazzles with a walk-in closet, and private bathroom. Step out back into your private oasis, surrounded by a vinyl privacy fence without any neighbors behind you. This backyard sets back to the newly opened "Joe Coviello" Nature Park with walking trails, a boardwalk, pond and an outdoor classroom. A nature lover's paradise. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home in a prime location in walking distance to top rated Cape Coral Schools and with easy access to everything SW Florida has to offer.
